Class GameObjectCollection<GO extends GameObject>

java.lang.Object

      com.escape.games.core.GameObjectCollection<GO>
Type Parameters:
GO - Target class for collection.
All Implemented Interfaces:
LoadedCallback, UnloadedCallback
public class GameObjectCollection<GO extends GameObject>
extends GameObject
implements LoadedCallback, UnloadedCallback

Container for component collection. Install pipeline: add incoming component to collection. Uninstall pipeline: remove incoming component from collection. The implementation uses both a list for sequential access, and a map for keyed access/membership-test.

Author:
escape-llc
